Cell["\<\
Some of the new bases of the invariant subspaces corresponding to the above \
standard Young tableaux have too many elements. It is because they are not \
orthogonal.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->747401877,ExpressionUUID->"4e2212fc-529e-4e94-afa0-8ba5989f912e"],

